items.title: Girardi, Yanks make 'strange' trip across town
items.summary: The Yanks' ride from Yankee Stadium to Citi Field on Monday at once seemed familiar from their annual visits to Queens and completely foreign in would be the Rays, not the Mets, waiting to play them there.
